Interface MSView<M>

  • All Known Implementing Classes:
    BlockUserActivity, EditMoodEventActivity, LoginActivity, MainActivity, MainFollowActivity, MoodHistoryActivity, NewMoodEventActivity, ViewMoodEventActivity

    public interface MSView<M>
    Main View class for MVC architecture for use in MoodSwing app. Created by nyitrai on 2/26/2017.

    • Method Summary

      All Methods Instance Methods Abstract Methods 
      Modifier and Type Method and Description
      void initialize()
      Each View, or android activity, should initialize all its widgets in this function, and also add itself to the Views tracked by the main Model class.
      void update(M model)
      Each View has an update method that reloads all the information from the Model that the View surfaces to the app's user.
